title: The Diablo IV Team on Doubling Down on Choices for Every Class

media:group.media:title: The Diablo IV Team on Doubling Down on Choices for Every Class
media:group.media:description: Diablo IV's Game Director Joe Shely and Diablo General Manager Rod Fergusson on how they're doubling down on unique class identities and giving players a wealth of options, without piling on complexity.
